algorithm
Start the program.

Display: "Welcome to MovieBot!"

Loop:

Take input from user (their message).

Use pattern matching to generate a response.

Display the chatbot response.

If user's input contains "book":

Ask movie name.

Ask number of tickets.

Ask preferred showtime.

Calculate total price (tickets × ₹150).

Display booking confirmation and total amount.

If user's input contains "bye", "exit", or "goodbye":

Exit the loop.

End the program.

flowchart
[Start]
   ↓
Display "Welcome to MovieBot!"
   ↓
[Input: User message]
   ↓
[Match input with patterns]
   ↓
Display Chatbot Response
   ↓
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│Is message related to "book tickets"?            │
│      └──> [Yes]                                 │
│             ↓                                   │
│     Ask Movie Name, Tickets, Showtime           │
│     Calculate Total = tickets × ₹150             │
│     Display Booking Confirmation                │
│                                                  │
│      └──> [No]                                   │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
   ↓
┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│Is message "bye"/"exit"/"goodbye"?            │
│      └──> [Yes]                              │
│             ↓                                │
│          [End]                               │
│      └──> [No]                               │
└────────────────────────────────────────────┘
   ↓
Loop back to [Input: User message]


